  "configuration":{"scope":"service","applyMode":"restart","schema":{"type":"object","additionalProperties":false,"required":["stateFile"],"properties":{"stateFile":{"type":"string","minLength":1,"maxLength":4096}}},"resourceController":{"protocol":"configuration.resource.v1"},"resourceCollections":[{"id":"delivery-profile","kind":"profile","title":"Webhook Delivery Profile","description":"企业验证码 Webhook 端点、允许渠道、超时和只写授权材料","schema":{"type":"object","additionalProperties":false,"required":["displayName","endpoint","channels","timeoutMs"],"properties":{"displayName":{"type":"string","minLength":1,"maxLength":160},"endpoint":{"type":"string","format":"uri","pattern":"^https://","maxLength":2048},"channels":{"type":"array","items":{"enum":["email","sms"]},"minItems":1,"maxItems":2,"uniqueItems":true},"timeoutMs":{"type":"integer","minimum":500,"maximum":15000,"default":5000}}},"managedCredentials":[{"id":"authorization","title":"Webhook Authorization","description":"仅写入，不返回浏览器；运行时通过 Material Lease 使用","purpose":"authentication.delivery.webhook","required":true}],"minItems":1,"maxItems":64}]},
